Charming full floor Victorian flat in vibrant Castro district. Classic San Francisco double parlor living and dining room, two bedrooms, remodeled kitchen, laundry room, closets, space for a home office, deck, and garage parking with storage. Period details like bay windows, wainscoting, and molding. It's a wonderful blend of traditional San Francisco living with modern touches. Walkout deck leads to shared backyard for outdoor grilling or sunbathing. Walk to amenities. .. Dolores Park, Whole Foods, The Verve, Kitchen Story, Duboce Triangle, outdoor recreation, and many shops and restaurants along Market St and Castro Street. Located in a 2-unit building on a desirable street. Home has been lovingly maintained but in need of upgrades. Great opportunity with upside potential.
